      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb driver\u2019s example, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox, sending power to the rear wheels via a GKN variable M-differential. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed control arm bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating common chassis fatigue. Maintenance is current, including a recent shim-and-bucket valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the paint exhibits minor stone chips from spirited use, the structural integrity and mechanical performance remain sharp, offering a pure, analog connection to the tarmac.",
